  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , we proved that under some assumptions about the performance of the classifier and the falsifier, our algorithm converges to an empty set of FNs. Although it may be difficult in practice to guarantee that these assumptions are satisfied, our algorithm performs reasonably well in practice, as shown in the next section.",
